'''Cinnabar Moon Retreat''' was a [[Spa/Legends|spa]] on [[Cinnabar Moon]] that had been abandoned due to the [[Yuuzhan Vong War]], and was used as the headquarters of the [[Wild Knights]]. It was seven levels tall, and offered [[Ando/Legends|Ando]] mud baths, geothermal spring baths, shops, restaurants, and [[Storm IV Twin-Pod cloud car/Legends|Storm IV Twin-Pod cloud car]] excursions. It was popular with [[Corulag/Legends|Corulag]] people.

